label: Chronometric Age Conversion Protocol (IRI)
rdfs_comment: The method used to convert the uncalibratedChronometricAge into a chronometric age in years, as captured in earliestChronometricAge, earliestChronometricAgeReferenceSystem, latestChronometricAge, and latestChronometricAgeReferenceSystem.
dcterms_description: Terms in the chronoiri namespace are intended to be used in RDF with non-literal objects.
